Data Notice
-----------
This software does not include any trade data. Users must obtain their own
data exports from UN COMTRADE (https://comtrade.un.org/) or equivalent
official sources. Users are responsible for complying with COMTRADE's terms
of use regarding data access, redistribution, and citation. No personal,
firm-level, or confidential data is processed by this software; it operates
exclusively on aggregate country-level trade statistics.

Disclaimer
----------
The analytical outputs produced by this software are descriptive indicators.
They do not constitute policy advice, legal guidance, or investment
recommendations. The authors assume no responsibility for decisions made on
the basis of outputs generated by this software.
